data.description: Cul de sac location! Home has 4 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 baths, great room, formal dining room (currently used as a playroom) and a large kitchen with a breakfast nook.  The kitchen has plenty of cabinet and counterspace, smooth top range, microwave, dishwasher, disposal and double bowl stainless steel sink.  Brushed nickel hardware throughout the entire home, fresh neutral paint and luxury plank flooring throughout most of the first level. Dining room is carpeted but owner has the LVP to match the rest of the home. Nice deck, huge fenced back yard. Single car garage with etched floor and built ins that convey, leads to side deck/porch with Canopy that will convey. This home is a must see, great house, location is convenient to schools, highways and shopping, make your appointment today!
